hardware-driver (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Hardware driver library for motor control
  * Supports velocity, position, and effort control modes
  * MIT mode (position + velocity + effort) support
  * Real-time motor status monitoring
  * Multi-threaded feedback processing
  * Simple API for easy integration

